author: arkurth
msg: Added sandbox/patches directory in order to make it easier to share and track patch files and other updated files in between releases.  This is by no means a proper method to handle patches.  It is just intended to be a slightly better way to handle situations where you want to share modified code as opposed to attaching it to an email.
Added vSphere_SDK_2.3.2_updated.pm. A description of the changes made to this file are included in the POD text.
